### GitHub API Examples
# Requires authentication token in environment variable GITHUB_TOKEN

@baseUrl = https://api.github.com

### Get user info
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_TOKEN}}

###

### List user repos
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/repos
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_TOKEN}}

###

### Get specific repo
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/charmbracelet/bubbletea

###

### Search repositories
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/repositories?q=language:go+stars:>1000&sort=stars&order=desc

###

### Get rate limit status
GET {{baseUrl}}/rate_limit

###

### Get GitHub status
GET https://www.githubstatus.com/api/v2/status.json